data.title: 10 Hotel Terbaik di Oui Jewellery, Victoria
data.meta_description: Temukan hotel terbaik di dekat Oui Jewellery di Victoria dengan ulasan, foto, dan peta asli. Pesan melalui Trip.com untuk mendapatkan harga terbaik dan tanpa biaya reservasi.
data.text:
Located in Victoria (Saanich Core), Accent Inns Victoria is within a 10-minute drive of Victoria Harbour and Victoria Clipper Ferry Terminal. This hotel is 10.4 mi (16.7 km) from Butchart Gardens and 2.4 mi (3.9 km) from Royal BC Museum. Take advantage of recreation opportunities such as a fitness center or take in the view from a terrace and a garden. Additional features at this hotel include complimentary wireless internet access, concierge services, and a fireplace in the lobby. At Accent Inns Victoria, enjoy a satisfying meal at the restaurant. Quench your thirst with your favorite drink at the bar/lounge. Featured amenities include a 24-hour business center, dry cleaning/laundry services, and a 24-hour front desk. Free self parking is available onsite. Make yourself at home in one of the 114 air-conditioned rooms featuring refrigerators. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and satellite programming is available for your entertainment. Private bathrooms with shower/tub combinations feature complimentary toiletries and hair dryers. Conveniences include desks and coffee/tea makers, and housekeeping is provided daily.

Selengkapnya

Embassy Inn is centrally located in Victoria, a 3-minute walk from Victoria Harbour and 6 minutes by foot from Royal BC Museum. This eco-certified hotel is 0.3 mi (0.6 km) from Victoria Clipper Ferry Terminal and 0.7 mi (1.1 km) from Victoria Fisherman's Wharf. Make use of convenient amenities such as complimentary wireless internet access, concierge services, and wedding services. Additional features at this Victorian hotel include a television in a common area, discounted use of a nearby fitness facility, and a vending machine. A complimentary buffet breakfast is served daily from 7 AM to 10:30 AM. Featured amenities include a 24-hour business center, complimentary newspapers in the lobby, and dry cleaning/laundry services. Self parking (subject to charges) is available onsite. Make yourself at home in one of the 70 air-conditioned rooms featuring refrigerators and LCD televisions. Rooms have private balconies. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and digital programming is available for your entertainment. Private bathrooms with shower/tub combinations feature complimentary toiletries and hair dryers.

Selengkapnya

With a stay at The Magnolia Hotel and Spa, you'll be centrally located in Victoria, steps from Government Street and within a 5-minute walk of Victoria Conference Centre. This eco-certified hotel is 0.3 mi (0.5 km) from Royal BC Museum and 0.5 mi (0.8 km) from Victoria Harbour. Relax at the full-service spa, where you can enjoy massages, body treatments, and facials. Additional features at this hotel include complimentary wireless internet access, a fireplace in the lobby, and bicycle tour information. Grab a bite to eat at The Courtney Room, a brasserie which features a bar/lounge, or stay in and take advantage of the room service (during limited hours). Continental breakfasts are available daily from 7:00 AM to 11:00 AM for a fee. Featured amenities include a business center, express check-out, and dry cleaning/laundry services. Planning an event in Victoria? This hotel has 1073 square feet (100 square meters) of space consisting of conference space and 3 meeting rooms. Make yourself at home in one of the 64 guestrooms featuring refrigerators and LCD televisions. Cable programming and iPod docking stations are provided for your entertainment, while complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected. Private bathrooms have designer toiletries and hair dryers. Conveniences include safes and desks, as well as phones with free local calls.

Selengkapnya

With a stay at Huntingdon Hotel and Suites, you'll be centrally located in Victoria, within a 5-minute walk of Victoria Harbour and Victoria Clipper Ferry Terminal. This eco-certified hotel is 0.4 mi (0.7 km) from Victoria Fisherman's Wharf and 0.5 mi (0.8 km) from Royal BC Museum. Pamper yourself with onsite massages, body treatments, and facials. Additional features at this hotel include complimentary wireless internet access, concierge services, and a fireplace in the lobby. Satisfy your appetite with local cuisine at Hunter's Club, one of the hotel's 2 restaurants. A complimentary buffet breakfast is served daily from 7:00 AM to 10:00 AM. Featured amenities include express check-out, dry cleaning/laundry services, and a 24-hour front desk. Self parking (subject to charges) is available onsite. Make yourself at home in one of the 113 air-conditioned rooms featuring refrigerators and flat-screen televisions. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and cable programming is available for your entertainment. Bathrooms have shower/tub combinations and hair dryers. Conveniences include safes and desks, as well as phones with free local calls.

Selengkapnya

We have what matters most at Four Points by Sheraton Victoria Gateway. Our extended-stay hotel near popular Langford sites is a short drive from Royal Roads University, golf courses at Bear Mountain Resort and hiking trails at Thetis Lake. Return from Millstream Village shops or Westshore activities to our lodging in Victoria, BC, with year-round swimming in an indoor pool or a 24-hour fitness centre with treadmills, ellipticals, row machines, free weights and yoga balls. Delicious meals with fresh ingredients await at Metropolitan Bar + Grill. If the weather allows, The Rooftop Patio at the MET serves beers, bites and some of the best views in Victoria, BC. Interested in hosting a large conference or a beautiful wedding? We offer a stylish ballroom with banquet seating for up to 350 guests. In your pet-friendly hotel room, enjoy free Wi-Fi, premium movie channels and work desks with ergonomic chairs. Rest assured, as the sun sets over Victoria, BC, Canada when you stay at Four Points by Sheraton.

Selengkapnya

Surpass your expectations for luxury at the newly renovated Delta Hotels Victoria Ocean Pointe Resort, located on the waterfront within a short stroll to downtown Victoria. Nestled on Victoria’s Harbour, our modern Victoria, BC, resort places you near attractions such as Butchart Gardens and the Royal British Columbia Museum with short walks to the Fisherman's Wharf and British Columbia Parliament Buildings. Explore downtown Victoria attractions and return to our hotel for stand-out meals at LURE Restaurant & Bar, offering amazing waterfront views. Maintain your routine in our fully equipped fitness centre, indoor pool and tennis courts. Relax and treat yourself at the Damara Day Spa with a massage or facial. Retreat to your newly renovated hotel room or suite, outfitted with a plush bed and stylish décor. In-room amenities include free high-speed Wi-Fi, 55" TVs and large desks with ergonomic chairs and plug-in panels. Make Delta Hotels Victoria Ocean Pointe Resort your gateway to the best of Victoria.

Selengkapnya

Located in Victoria (Burnside), Robin Hood Inn & Suites is within a 5-minute drive of Government Street and Save-On-Foods Memorial Centre. This eco-certified hotel is 2.1 mi (3.4 km) from Victoria Conference Centre and 2.3 mi (3.6 km) from Royal BC Museum. Take in the views from a terrace and a garden and make use of amenities such as complimentary wireless internet access. This hotel also features concierge services, an arcade/game room, and a fireplace in the lobby. A complimentary continental breakfast is served daily from 6:30 AM to 10:30 AM. Featured amenities include complimentary wired internet access, a computer station, and express check-out. Free self parking is available onsite. Make yourself at home in one of the 55 guestrooms featuring refrigerators. Your pillowtop bed comes with down comforters and premium bedding. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and digital programming is available for your entertainment. Private bathrooms with showers feature complimentary toiletries and hair dryers.

Selengkapnya

With a stay at Helms Inn, you'll be centrally located in Victoria, just a 4-minute walk from Royal BC Museum and 9 minutes by foot from Victoria Harbour. This hotel is 0.6 mi (1 km) from Victoria Clipper Ferry Terminal and 12.6 mi (20.3 km) from Butchart Gardens. Take in the views from a garden and make use of amenities such as complimentary wireless internet access and a vending machine. Featured amenities include a computer station, a 24-hour front desk, and luggage storage. Self parking (subject to charges) is available onsite. Make yourself at home in one of the 48 guestrooms, featuring kitchenettes with refrigerators and stovetops. Complimentary wired and wireless internet access keeps you connected, and cable programming provides entertainment. Conveniences include safes and desks, as well as phones with free local calls.

Selengkapnya
